{"word":"περιδέξιος","slug":"περιδέξιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>περιδέξιος</b></el> <el>(περι-δέξιος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἀμφιδέξιος'><el>ἀμφιδέξιος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>with two right hands</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i.e.</a> <i>using both hands alike</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>very dexterous</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}